{"tid":1021900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天星小輪女乘客墮海　維港海陸空大搜索","createTime":"2019-02-14T14:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T09:38:22.000Z","uid":41404,"like":214,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3660a9d7e0ce38d0aeb7ce47c036feca9b9299","tid":1021900,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"晚上8時許，有人由天星小輪墮海，職員見狀於是報警。水警輪、消防船等到現場搜索，而消防人員亦分別在岸上及下海搜尋，及至晚上約10時，飛行服務隊出動直升機在上空盤旋搜索，惟仍未尋回墮海人士。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，一名女子由尖沙嘴登上小輪，前往中環，惟小輪駛離碼頭約50米後，有人見到該名女子突然由小輪跳下，未知她因何事墮海。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/295080/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F295080%2F&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=8f022e5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/295080/</a>"},{"pid":"57bc7afab603d30337a4c782b9c079870719d360","tid":1021900,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865c823b2d8ce07cf020e2d75b2faa795c5a98b4","tid":1021900,"uid":223959,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08979952917a3cbdeec9a96f640898524c7b83db","tid":1021900,"uid":41404,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"晚上8時許，一名身穿紅色衫的女子乘搭天星小輪由尖沙嘴往中環，其間她突然情緒激動，跳入海中，船員發現後立即停船並報警。水警輪及消防船現正於現場搜索，飛行服務隊亦在上空協助。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=56bbb508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190214/59260816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59260816&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=8c0ee130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190214%2F59260816&h=6cf3e354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190214/59260816</a>"},{"pid":"2c48bdf0c6fb62133b8bc910bd5218040ab94f9a","tid":1021900,"uid":38456,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"恐怖在線又多左野講"},{"pid":"ac6450feebcb3ac544ef5a23a754eba95d19eb18","tid":1021900,"uid":78873,"like":234,"dislike":14,"score":220,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"咁邪 第時座船過海無啦啦船尾坐住個紅衣女子見唔到樣 都咪話唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db7a1cda0438c815abeb7d0c38b8fc295b98afb","tid":1021900,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"香港開埠以黎第一次"},{"pid":"95ec8260b5f37d678102b8d013ce1893de5d789f","tid":1021900,"uid":63113,"like":354,"dislike":0,"score":354,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"情人節紅衫跳海 咁睇唔開"},{"pid":"9be3c9982135b148f785e7478ec08c037fb08d2c","tid":1021900,"uid":34410,"like":98,"dislike":2,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"累撚死人揾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b920fb08219863c30e3112cb89db42831f11b139","tid":1021900,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:44:56.000Z","msg"